    quellen: ['White, M. & Epston, D. (1990). Narrative Means to Therapeutic Ends. Norton.', 'Morgan, A. (2000). What is Narrative Therapy? Dulwich Centre Publications.', 'Ncube, N. (2006). The Tree of Life Project. International Journal of Narrative Therapy and Community Work.']
